    {"id":"2fb1ca43-55c3-8035-b7b6-d7f372ed6539","notionUrl":"https://www.notion.so/2fb1ca4355c38035b7b6d7f372ed6539","name":"Pay as you go","date":"2026-02-16","content":"**Adapty is free until you hit $5,000 in monthly revenue, with full access to everything.** Starting today, you get the full Adapty growth toolkit — free — until your app reaches $5,000 in tracked monthly revenue. We're not offering a \"lite\" version with gated features. You get full access to Paywall Builder, A/B testing, analytics, and add-ons — exactly as larger apps do. If your monthly revenue is under $5K, the cost is $0. When you cross that threshold, the model shifts to a simple 1% of revenue, so pricing scales fairly with your growth. 👉 Explore the new pricing: https://adapty.io/pricing","tags":[],"needsAuthorInput":false,"needsEventDetails":false,"authorIdsToTag":[]},
